org.apache.poi.hssf.record

Class RecordInputStream.LeftoverDataException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • java.lang.RuntimeException
          • org.apache.poi.hssf.record.RecordInputStream.LeftoverDataException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Enclosing class:
    RecordInputStream

    public static final class RecordInputStream.LeftoverDataException
extends java.lang.RuntimeException
    For use in BiffViewer which may construct Records that don't completely read all available data. This exception should never be thrown otherwise.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
Shall be called with ValueRangeRecord, AxisLineFormatRecord, FrameRecord, AxisOptionsRecord, OldLabelRecord, HyperlinkRecord, DatRecord, CellRangeAddressList, AreaRecord, LeftMarginRecord, CFRuleRecord, ChartEndObjectRecord, PageBreakRecord, FontBasisRecord, FontIndexRecord, AreaFormatRecord, UserSViewEnd, DataFormatRecord, RightMarginRecord, UnitsRecord, AutoFilterInfoRecord, ChartStartObjectRecord, AxisRecord, FormulaRecord, CFHeader12Record, WSBoolRecord, ChartTitleFormatRecord, NumberFormatIndexRecord, AbstractEscherHolderRecord, BarRecord, ChartStartBlockRecord, SeriesChartGroupIndexRecord, ObjRecord, PageBreakRecord.Break, OldCellRecord, VerticalPageBreakRecord, CFRule12Record, SheetPropertiesRecord, SCLRecord, LineFormatRecord, ObjectLinkRecord, BottomMarginRecord, ChartFRTInfoRecord, MulRKRecord, UseSelFSRecord, HorizontalPageBreakRecord, HeaderFooterRecord, CellRecord, SeriesToChartGroupRecord, PlotGrowthRecord, DConRefRecord, OldStringRecord, TopMarginRecord, CFHeaderRecord, PrintSetupRecord, CategorySeriesAxisRecord, FontFormatting, LabelRecord, SeriesRecord, TickRecord, TextRecord.
